# Semgrep integration rules

When semgrep MCP is available:
- Run semgrep scan after EVERY file modification.
- Fix all ERROR and WARNING findings before continuing.
- Never mark a finding as acceptable without explicit user approval.

When semgrep is not available, mentally apply:
- python.lang.security.audit.formatted-sql-query
- python.jwt.security.jwt-none-alg
- python.flask.security.hardcoded-secret
- generic.secrets.security.detected-generic-secret